  ItemName: Near-fatal damage teleports you to safety
  ItemDesc: Whenever you take nonfatal damage that leaves you under 20% of your health,
    you immediately gather your powers to teleport to a random room on your Drifter.
    You also restore 50 health. This effect has a very long cooldown that decreases
    with your ALCHEMY.
